docs {
  ## Get Sync Status

  Returns last sync statistics:
  - lastFullSync: DateTime of last sync
  - itemsScanned: Number of items processed
  - syncDuration: Duration in milliseconds

  Returns null values if no sync has been performed yet.

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ Returns sync status or "No sync performed" message
  - ✅ Requires admin authentication
}
